sequenceDiagram
    title SD-01: User Login & Authentication Flow

    actor User
    participant Frontend as Dashboard (Frontend)
    participant AuthAPI as Auth API (/api/auth)
    participant DB as Database
    participant AuditSvc as Audit Service

    User->>Frontend: Enter username & password
    Frontend->>AuthAPI: POST /api/auth/login {username, password}
    AuthAPI->>DB: Query user by username
    DB-->>AuthAPI: Return user record

    alt User not found
        AuthAPI-->>Frontend: 401 Unauthorized - User not found
        Frontend-->>User: Show error message
    else User found
        AuthAPI->>AuthAPI: bcrypt.verify(password, hash)
        alt Password incorrect
            AuthAPI-->>Frontend: 401 Unauthorized - Invalid credentials
            Frontend-->>User: Show error message
        else Password correct
            AuthAPI->>AuthAPI: Generate JWT token (expires 24h)
            AuthAPI->>AuditSvc: Log USER_LOGIN event
            AuditSvc->>DB: INSERT audit_log (action=USER_LOGIN)
            DB-->>AuditSvc: Confirm
            AuthAPI-->>Frontend: 200 OK {token, user_info}
            Frontend->>Frontend: Store JWT in localStorage
            Frontend-->>User: Redirect to Dashboard
        end
    end
